articles.title: Sienna Miller Shuts Down Criticism Over 14-Year Age Gap With Boyfriend Oli Green - HuffPost
articles.description: The "American Woman" star is expecting a baby girl with the 27-year-old actor.
articles.content:
Sienna Miller says she's "never been able" to "legislate on matters of the heart."
Sienna Miller isnt worried about what the haters have to say about her 14-year age gap with her partner, Oli Green.… [+4107 chars]
